<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Error 404</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/style.css">
  <style>
    .error-404 {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 80vh;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .error-404 h1 {
      font-size: 6rem;
      color: var(--focus-color, #0069be);
      margin-bottom: 0.5em;
    }
    .error-404 p {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--letter-color, #424242);
      margin-bottom: 2em;
    }
    .error-404 a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1em;
      padding: 0.75em 2em;
      background: var(--focus-color, #0069be);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 7px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .error-404 a:hover {
      background: #004b88e7;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container error-404">
    <h1>404</h1>
    <p>A página que você procura não existe.</p>
    <a href="./">Voltar para a página inicial</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>